---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const effectiveDate = "May 17, 2026";
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use · Gerard Agba" description="Terms of use for gerardagba.com.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-24">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[color:var(--color-accent)] mb-4">Terms</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-2">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">Effective: {effectiveDate}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert mt-10 max-w-none space-y-6 text-[color:var(--color-fg)] leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">1. Use of free workflow templates</h2>
      <p>
        Workflow JSON files, setup guides, and walkthroughs distributed via
        this site are licensed for your own commercial and personal use. You
        may modify them. You may not resell them or republish them as a paid
        product or course.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">2. No warranty</h2>
      <p>
        Templates are provided <strong>&ldquo;as-is.&rdquo;</strong> They are reference implementations,
        not certified production code. You are responsible for testing them
        against your own data before relying on them for financial reporting,
        compliance, or any other business-critical purpose.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">3. Paid services</h2>
      <p>
        Paid engagements (workflow installs, custom builds) are governed by
        a separate Statement of Work signed at engagement start. Nothing on
        this site constitutes a binding offer or contract.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">4. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, I am not liable for any
        indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use
        of free templates or this website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">5. Changes</h2>
      <p>
        These terms may be updated. The effective date above will change
        when they do. Continued use after a change means you accept the
        updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">6. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions: <a href="mailto:hello@gerardagba.com" class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">hello@gerardagba.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
